race.comment: ZIPPER ON TIME (1) has a superb record at this track and trip, unbeaten so far from seven starts. Recorded a 1.5 lengths win (29.45) in a NG last time at this track. Has the ability and should feature. HE'S A PEARL (8) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led throughout to score when a 5 length winner (29.67) over 520m at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Likely to be in the finish. FEARLESS BANDIT (7) can keep on winning after a head turning last start success, getting around the 520m at this track in 29.65. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. BACK TOMORROW (2) is a course and distance winner who cannot be left out of calculations.
